Code 1

class Solution {
    public int smallestNumber(int n) {
        int ans = 0;
        
        for(int i=0; n>0; i++) {
            ans += power(i);
            n = n >> 1;
        }

        return ans;
    }

    private int power(int i) {
        return 1 << i;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(log n)
Space Complexity : O(1)

Code 2

class Solution {
    public int smallestNumber(int n) {
        int res = n;
        while((res & (res + 1)) != 0) {
            res++;
        }
        return res;
    }
}

Time Complexity : 
Space Complexity : O()
